name: one. two. three. end.
description:
one. two. three. end. is my first game upload (haha help me), made for the Low Effort Jam 22!

With MANY levels, each one ranging from simple to ridiculous difficulty, stunning graphics and ultra soft soundtrack, this masterpiece is ready to take the next GOTY award. And it's completely free!

Seriously though, this apparently effortless Jam encouraged me enough to make me work on a game project from start to finish, and publish it, and I'm really grateful for that! This project, even if super basic, proved to be such a good test for all the programming skills learned in the past months, but never really put into a real-world-like situation.

So yeah, low effort, but still big effort! Make sure to let me know what you think of the game (lmao), but also stay tuned for (hopefully) better and bigger projects! Bye :)
